Since the Halloween is coming, FLORA is on her way to Eggplant 1 with a giant basket. 
In this morning, Jing spent over 2 hours to dress up like a 5 year old girl.


FLORA finished her work, then she went to washroom. She looked in the mirror, and she saw a huge bald head -- and it was hers.
FLORA was so scared, she was running and screaming, seeking for the exit!
